### Health
GET http://localhost:8083/actuator/health

### List files through Kong
GET http://localhost:18000/api/files
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Request-Id: file-demo-list-001

### Upload file through Kong
POST http://localhost:18000/api/files
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Request-Id: file-demo-upload-001
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=Boundary

--Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello from Master Data Portal file demo.
--Boundary--

### Download file through Kong
GET http://localhost:18000/api/files/{{file_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Request-Id: file-demo-download-001

### Delete file through Kong
DELETE http://localhost:18000/api/files/{{file_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Request-Id: file-demo-delete-001
